casebody.data:
Wonga MAQAGI, petitioner,
v.
HORIZON LAMPS, INC., et al. No. 16-8470. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 2, 2017.

Motion of petitioner for reconsideration of order denying leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. The order entered May 30, 2017, is vacated. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.
